  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1275380/extras/79335479fc73c3b91754d7767e95c557.avif?t=1726493009\" width=600 height=142 /></span><br><br>In <strong>Emergency Call 112 Showroom</strong>, you have the opportunity to look at all currently done vehicles from<strong> Emergency Call 112 – The Fire Fighting Simulation 2</strong> in detail for the first time. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1275380/extras/3312f0afb4f2241b7cd816f5d8692a5f.webp?t=1726493009\" width=600 height=43 /></span><br><br>The <strong>Emergency Call 112 Showroom</strong> offers you the possibility to design and implement your own textures and share them with the community via the [Steam Workshop].<br>Compare notes with other gamers and build the textures of your fire fighting station so that it is ready for the main game. <br><br><i>To edit the Texture we recommend to use Adobe Photoshop / GIMP /  - make sure to save the file as DXT1 DDS and Mipmaps (maybe require a plugin) and mirror the image vertical before export!</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1275380/extras/3312f0afb4f2241b7cd816f5d8692a5f.webp?t=1726493009\" width=600 height=43 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1275380/extras/79335479fc73c3b91754d7767e95c557.avif?t=1726493009\" width=600 height=142 /></span><br><br>In <strong>Emergency Call 112 Showroom</strong>, you have the opportunity to look at all currently done vehicles from<strong> Emergency Call 112 – The Fire Fighting Simulation 2</strong> in detail for the first time. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1275380/extras/3312f0afb4f2241b7cd816f5d8692a5f.webp?t=1726493009\" width=600 height=43 /></span><br><br>The <strong>Emergency Call 112 Showroom</strong> offers you the possibility to design and implement your own textures and share them with the community via the [Steam Workshop].<br>Compare notes with other gamers and build the textures of your fire fighting station so that it is ready for the main game. <br><br><i>To edit the Texture we recommend to use Adobe Photoshop / GIMP /  - make sure to save the file as DXT1 DDS and Mipmaps (maybe require a plugin) and mirror the image vertical before export!</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1275380/extras/3312f0afb4f2241b7cd816f5d8692a5f.webp?t=1726493009\" width=600 height=43 /></span>",
